Dialogue: 0,0:24:34.28,0:24:37.12,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We don't know anything about\NMarika-chan's early life.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:37.12,0:24:39.62,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I end up making Marika-chan angry.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:39.62,0:24:42.12,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Suzuki-kun cheers me up nonchalantly.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:42.12,0:24:44.87,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,My past is connected to the Shishigou accident...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:44.87,0:24:50.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Many things have happened, but I believe everyone will\Nbe able to understand each other much, much better soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:50.46,0:24:53.47,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then, one day, Marika-chan fainted.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:53.47,0:24:57.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Next time on Twin Spica:\NAlone.
